This is the area corresponding to the AL Sea. The second and third maps are inspired from [[Summer 2014 Event]] E-1 and E-2.<br>
There is no repair dock by default on this hexagon however it is expandable up to two.<br>
:Fully clearing this area, alongside [[Kancolle Kai:Sandbox/Area 12#/V12-4|V12-4]] gives acces to [[KanColle Kai:Sandbox/Area 15#/V15-1|V15-1]] ('''深海棲地後方''').

